CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 10, 1966, pg. 1B reads: " 'I Want That'...is what little Cheryl Beaman is telling her aunt, Mrs. Norma Bonner while her cousin, Michelle Bonner hugs a beautiful doll that she would like for Santa to bring her on Christmas."
TitMainTitle: Mrs. Norma Bonner, standing with Cheryl Beaman and cousin Michelle Bonner holding a doll, standing in Toyland on ninth floor of Kaufmann's Department Store
